Instalacion del proyetco:
composer create-project laravel/laravel control-activos-pihcsa
cd control-activos-pihcsa
composer require laravel/breeze --dev (Autenticacion)
php artisan breeze:install (Css)
npm install
npm run dev

2.-Instalacion de la plantilla
composer require jeroennoten/laravel-adminlte
php artisan adminlte:install
